    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/51e2f3dd374507ccf692778afd4ee420.poster.avif?t=1719838364\" width=600 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/51e2f3dd374507ccf692778afd4ee420.webm?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/51e2f3dd374507ccf692778afd4ee420.mp4?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><br>你可以在Detached的测试版中体验提取包裹战斗。使用EVA宇航服的高级模块进行战斗，争夺宝贵的包裹。计谋与对敌人攻击的预判是赢取战斗的关键。<br>在测试版中，你可以在一张地图里体验跨平台玩家对战模式，与非VR、PC VR、PSVR、Oculus Rift的完整版游戏玩家进行对战。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/d1d410b947cb7e8d6b4a15092077a1a3.poster.avif?t=1719838364\" width=600 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/d1d410b947cb7e8d6b4a15092077a1a3.webm?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/d1d410b947cb7e8d6b4a15092077a1a3.mp4?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><br>在Detached中通过跨平台玩家对战模式与其他玩家对战！与SteamVR、PC非VR、PSVR、Oculus版本的PC与VR玩家争夺胜利。在“提取包裹”的激励战斗中，玩家将争夺位于地图一角的货物。使用各种手段攻击你的对手，取得优势。避开攻击，安全回到基地。在“竞速”模式中穿梭太空。凭借机敏与环境预判力在小行星群与航天飞机碎片之间穿梭。走错一步即可丧命。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/ca4fa9a2a1c52326c9b925d1ada64e2b.poster.avif?t=1719838364\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/ca4fa9a2a1c52326c9b925d1ada64e2b.webm?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/ca4fa9a2a1c52326c9b925d1ada64e2b.mp4?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/cb673b746a3fd56c8a5199e48e64ebbf.poster.avif?t=1719838364\" width=600 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/cb673b746a3fd56c8a5199e48e64ebbf.webm?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/cb673b746a3fd56c8a5199e48e64ebbf.mp4?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><br>在残酷的未来宇宙中，一度繁荣的太空殖民地因长年战乱而被摧毁，成为废墟。在不断的威胁中求得生存成了文明的法则。不得杀戮这条人类最后的律法也逐渐失去效力。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/5cf482ddc3efeb435f2b0c80b1259b7b.poster.avif?t=1719838364\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/5cf482ddc3efeb435f2b0c80b1259b7b.webm?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/5cf482ddc3efeb435f2b0c80b1259b7b.mp4?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><br>你依靠在太空收集有价值的金属矿物为生。一度繁荣的巨大太空船是收集矿物的最佳场所。不幸的是，这个世界的一切都无法预知……<br><br>你必须面对死亡的威胁，在残酷的宇宙中生存。在太空中无所依靠的你，必须迅速掌握在零引力环境中的操控。你可以通过高级EVA宇航服探索周围的环境。你必须在与敌人的战斗中求生并等待救援，同时发现新的谜团，在被遗弃的太空站探索未知领域。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/a77195940ac61e4652d57ced9ee160d2.poster.avif?t=1719838364\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/a77195940ac61e4652d57ced9ee160d2.webm?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/a77195940ac61e4652d57ced9ee160d2.mp4?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/a27308dab8deebfc028048545e02eacd.poster.avif?t=1719838364\" width=600 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/a27308dab8deebfc028048545e02eacd.webm?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/a27308dab8deebfc028048545e02eacd.mp4?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>自由体验</strong>——在沙盒环境中体验完全自由的运动。<br></li><li><strong>逼真氛围</strong>——探索受引力启发而设计的太空世界，欣赏由Mikołaj Stroiński（The Witcher 3、The Vanishing of Ethan Carter、Sniper Ghost Warrior 3）作曲的管弦配乐。<br></li><li><strong>爆炸、碎片、冲击</strong>——在单机与跨平台玩家对战模式中使用盾牌、加速及EMP火箭能力。用内置EVA宇航服的定位导弹摧毁目标。掌握武器的准备时间，不让敌人占得先机。通过盾牌技巧暂时免于敌人攻击。利用加速隧道获得速度优势。<br></li><li><strong>宇航员训练</strong>——掌握在零引力环境中的模拟驾驶操控。穿上宇航服，进入难忘的虚空之旅！<br></li><li><strong>不容眨眼的激烈战斗</strong>——在Detached令人心跳加速的跨平台玩家对战模式中与敌人对战，或在单机模式中体验无限的宇宙虚空。优化的多玩家模式为使用Oculus Rift、HTC Vive、PlayStation VR、PC版本的玩家提供了两个游戏模式。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/b70a8fd83138bd38138d20c57af4ee5c.poster.avif?t=1719838364\" width=600 height=38 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/b70a8fd83138bd38138d20c57af4ee5c.webm?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/b70a8fd83138bd38138d20c57af4ee5c.mp4?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><br>探索。对战。幸存。这是在遥远太空中生存的法则。在Detached中，你将来到因人类的暴政与剥削而被破坏的宇宙一角。长年的战乱与贪婪，摧毁了遥远太空的人类殖民地。利益集团分崩瓦解，腐败企业纷纷解体。<br>大部分人坚守着人类仅存的生存法则：不得杀戮。然而在匮乏资源、漫无边际的宇宙深处，不少人仍会为了生存而不择手段。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/bac601e20716ba57124dd0bf4d0831ba.poster.avif?t=1719838364\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/bac601e20716ba57124dd0bf4d0831ba.webm?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895530/extras/bac601e20716ba57124dd0bf4d0831ba.mp4?t=1719838364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><br>Detached不仅是一款游戏，更是一种体验。为了完成游戏，你必须掌握EVA宇航服的操控，学会在逼真的零引力环境中移动。<br><br>VR玩家的需求明确：他们期待VR设备给予他们更强烈的，之前被认为难以企及的游戏体验。Detached让玩家感受到极端的紧张氛围。现在，没有VR设备的玩家也能通过Detached的非VR版得到类似的游戏体验！<br><br>在Detached的非VR版本中体验太空世界！完全沉浸在至此仅拥有VR设备的玩家才能体验到的逼真的未来太空世界。在单机模式中体验未知的巨型太空站边缘，或在跨平台玩家对战模式中与敌人对战。与SteamVR、PC测试版、PSVR、Oculus Rift的玩家对战！",
